messages.text: Blue polka dot blouse, three seats behind you, literally asked you for your number in geometry today
cause I knew I’d inevitably forget what the homework questions were
Correct on the first try! One shot wonder over here ;)
But I don’t think I could ever top Mr. Nardone’s daily wardrobe
That mustard yellow one is more mustard yellow than actual mustard
He literally wears shower slippers to class
I hear he used to show up in class in his bathrobe
Got a B- on my chem midterm
Mike Foisy kept staring at me in English
He is literally the creepiest guy ever
If we’re going to be honest, all boys are creepy
Are you going to the dance next week?
Yeah but I don’t have a date
Don’t worry, neither do I. We can be dateless together
I was really nervous before asking for your number today
Idk. There’s just something about you
Well I’m really glad I gave it to you
Well thank you. Blushing through my phone screen right now
Hahaha I’m honored I could make you do that
My dad’s calling me for dinner so I better go
I’ll see you in class tomorrow?
Don’t you want the questions for the geometry homework?
Hey I’m outside the dance right now, where are you?!
Hurry up, I’m standing alone here in the corner looking like an idiot
Oh shut up and just get here already!
I’m pulling into the parking lot!
Is that you? In the periwrinkle dress?
I don’t really know how to say this
But I don’t think I can last another second keeping it inside
I’m in love with you. I have been since the first day I laid eyes on you in Nardone’s class
I know this is out of nowhere and you’ll probably never talk to me again but I just really wanted to let you know
I’m in love with you too
Well not since the first day of Nardone’s class. But I know I’ve never felt this way about anyone else
I have an aunt they disowned once she came out of the closet
She lives in New York now but they don’t talk at all
Well that doesn’t change the way I feel about you at all
It doesn’t change the way I feel about you either
I guess there’s just one solution
We’ll just have to be secretly in love with each other
Omg where have you been?! I’ve been texting and calling for days
And where were you in school? I stopped by your house but all the lights were out
My parents read all our texts and they know
I’m texting you from my brother’s phone right now
They pulled me out of school and they’re going to ship me to Eton
I’ve basically been a prisoner in my own house
We need to break you out
Would your aunt in New York take us in do you think?
Well I have a plan. Do you trust me?
I need you to sneak out of your house tonight with a suitcase of your favorite clothes
and meet me at the train station at 10:30
You mean more to me than they ever will
I’ll see you in a little bit babe. Remember 10:30 don’t be late
Where are you?? The train’s about to leave in five minutes
I had to wait until my parents fell asleep
There’re headlights behind me right now
He got out of the car but I’m running through the bushes
I can hear his footsteps right behind me
Just a little bit further babe
